title: november 28: maia on magellan (with Jake Luppen of Hippo Campus)
description:
In this episode of 365 days with mxmtoon, Maia talks about an incredible journey: the sea voyage that was the first to circumnavigate the world, and along the way, discovered the Strait of Magellan, which was crossed for the first time today in 1520. She is also joined by Jake Luppen from the band Hippo Campus to talk about his big homestate show. Listen to this episode today and make sure you’re following along with the daily updates @365daysmxmtoon on all platforms.
